scheduled_maintenances.name: [GRA/BHS][Public cloud] - End Of Life ML Serving

incident_updates.body: Start time : 16/08/2022 15:00 UTC End time : 01/12/2022 08:00 UTC Comment : As part of the product lifecycle management, We will end the Sales of ML Serving services October 4th 2022 (no more new services). We will end the Growth of existing ML Serving services December 1st 2022 (no more new namespaces or models deployed). We will end the Support of all ML Serving services December 1st 2022 (shutdown of the services and related backups). Impacted customers will be notified by email about this End-Of-Life process in August (email from NIC Admin) Perimeter: - All ML Serving services and solutions (free or paid) worldwide. - OVHcloud /cloud/project/{serviceName}/ai/serving/* API endpoints NOT in the perimeter: - AI Notebooks - AI Training - AI Deploy (formerly AI Apps) Workaround: customer will be contacted to migrate to new Public Cloud Databases AI Deploy. Migration tutorials will be provided on https://docs.ovh.com/gb/en/publiccloud/ai/ Timeline: 04/10/2022 10h CEST : End of Sales 01/12/2022 10h CEST : End of Growth 01/12/2022 10h CEST : End of Support, Shutdown of all impacted services 10h CEST We will update this task during the proposed timeline.
